are the mangas you lent me. Thank you very much.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Whoa~, you read them all already? That was quick. There were ten plus volumes~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"Well~, they were just so good that I ended up flying through them.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"It is quite the interesting manga series, isn't it~? So, what part gave you the most feels~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"Hmm, a lot of parts did, but I'd have to go with the end of volume seven~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"I had a feeling the hat the main character always wore was fishy, but I never expected removing it would teleport everyone and Earth itself to another dimension.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Yeah, that was pretty unpredictable, all right~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"Suddenly going from a relaxing slice-of-life story to a battle adventure was another thing I didn't see coming at all~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"That part also really blew me away the first time I read the manga~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"And the part where the demon lord, dragon, and the hat join forces to fight against the god was pretty exciting, wasn't it~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"Yes, it really was~. Friendship, hard work, mystery, action. The manga has it all~. It's incredible.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev177-ep4-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"The wai